18:59.181 --> 19:00.170
So?

19:00.982 --> 19:02.711
Where is everybody?

19:07.656 --> 19:08.723
Welcome to the official opening
of the first day...

19:08.723 --> 19:10.884
Welcome to the official opening
of the first day...

19:10.959 --> 19:13.359
of the Baby-sitters Club Summer Day Camp.

