How old is Jimmy-Tony?

20:07.682 --> 20:10.310
Jimmy-Tony, they want to know
how old you are.

20:12.454 --> 20:14.183
He´s the same age as me.

20:15.323 --> 20:18.019
Well, then he gets a red one, too.

20:18.093 --> 20:19.321
Come on.

20:20.495 --> 20:22.986
-Okay, he´s paid.
-Kristy, look.

20:23.064 --> 20:25.259
Green. Same as you.

20:25.333 --> 20:27.096
-What do we got?
-Can l have one?

20:27.169 --> 20:28.227
What?

20:28.303 --> 20:30.464
She said she wants a potholder.

20:34.042 --> 20:35.270
See you.

20:36.678 --> 20:39.806
My mom was wondering,
well, there´s two of us...

20:39.881 --> 20:41.405
and l was wondering, too.

20:41.483 --> 20:45.249
My mom and dad talked, and they
don´t think me and my sister should come...

20:45.320 --> 20:48.483
because it´ll be too much money,
so l was wondering:

20:48.557 --> 20:52.493
Since my sister´s so small,
could we both get in for the price of one?

20:53.128 --> 20:54.993
l´ve been to the moon.

21:03.405 --> 21:04.804
Over there!

21:17.018 --> 21:20.215
On your mark! Get set! Go!

21:20.288 --> 21:22.483
Come on, you guys! Come on!

21:25.160 --> 21:27.526
Come on, guys! Go!

21:29.431 --> 21:31.956
-l´ve got to go to the bathroom!
-Me, too!

21:33.535 --> 21:34.900
Bathroom?

