22:22.250 --> 22:25.048
-Okay, turn. Good.
-You sure you don´t need any help?

22:25.120 --> 22:29.113
-l think you all should think about it.
-´Cause this is my last offer.

22:30.458 --> 22:32.153
Sounds like your first offer.

22:32.227 --> 22:36.664
l´d snap him up if l was you all,
´cause he´s really great with the kids.

22:36.865 --> 22:39.698
-How much would you want?
-Not much.

22:40.001 --> 22:41.491
Like how much?

22:41.836 --> 22:43.303
Like nothing.

22:43.638 --> 22:45.936
-When can you start?
-Yesterday.

22:47.976 --> 22:49.967
-You got a deal.
-Kristy!

22:50.578 --> 22:52.569
-He´s a dweeb.
-He´s a free dweeb.

22:52.647 --> 22:54.547
Yeah, l´m a free dweeb.

22:59.220 --> 23:02.383
l said get her a flower,
not squirt her with one.

23:02.957 --> 23:04.117
Right.

23:06.094 --> 23:07.254
Sorry.

23:08.930 --> 23:11.262
Logan said he wouldn´t have gone
with Cokie.

23:11.333 --> 23:14.097
