What would you have done?

23:14.169 --> 23:16.603
-Nothing.
-You couldn´t do nothing!

23:16.671 --> 23:18.866
lf he wants to do something,
l can´t stop him.

23:18.940 --> 23:22.273
Yes, you can. You can tell somebody
when you´re ticked off.

23:22.344 --> 23:24.938
We can´t let men get away with everything.

23:28.249 --> 23:29.978
Kristy, hi.

23:30.985 --> 23:32.509
-How you doing?
-Dad?

23:37.158 --> 23:38.819
