23:40.128 --> 23:43.359
-A while ago. You must be Kristy´s friend.
-Mary Anne.

23:44.132 --> 23:46.930
Sure, you´re Richard Spier´s little girl.

23:47.969 --> 23:49.937
l´d better go.

23:50.004 --> 23:52.165
lt was nice seeing you again, Mr. Thomas.

23:52.240 --> 23:53.264
Patrick.

23:53.641 --> 23:56.166
-Call me, or l´ll call you.
-Call me.

23:59.647 --> 24:01.979
