Didn´t you get my postcard?
l said l´d be coming.

24:07.222 --> 24:09.656
Dad, you always say you´ll be coming.

24:16.164 --> 24:17.688
You look great.

24:18.700 --> 24:20.691
l mean, what, it´s been....

24:21.169 --> 24:23.103
l mean, you were....

24:27.542 --> 24:29.737
So how was school this year?

24:29.811 --> 24:31.574
-Okay.
-Did you like it?

24:31.846 --> 24:33.575
-Yeah.
-Did you get good grades?

24:33.648 --> 24:34.910
Guess so.

24:36.584 --> 24:39.144
