24:55.069 --> 24:56.297
Do what?

24:56.938 --> 24:58.929
-l´m moving back.
-You are?

24:59.407 --> 25:02.604
Yeah, l have a shot at a sports column
with The News.

25:03.144 --> 25:06.807
l didn´t want to say anything
till it was a sure thing, but l....

25:06.881 --> 25:09.179
You know, l couldn´t resist seeing you.

25:09.250 --> 25:10.945
Have you seen Mom?

25:13.988 --> 25:15.216
Not yet.

25:17.258 --> 25:19.385
She´s probably in the house.

25:21.529 --> 25:25.693
l don´t want her to really know l´m here yet.
Not till l hear about the job, okay?

25:25.767 --> 25:28.327
Think we could keep it a secret
for a couple of days?

25:28.403 --> 25:29.392
l guess.

25:33.274 --> 25:34.366
Good.

25:42.116 --> 25:45.085
l like your hair long. lt looks really cool.

25:47.222 --> 25:50.749
l´ll be staying at the Strathmore lnn
if you want to reach me.

25:50.825 --> 25:53.225
And don´t forget, l owe you a pizza.

25:53.294 --> 25:55.319
Still like anchovies best?

25:56.097 --> 25:57.086
Yeah?

25:58.066 --> 25:59.055
Okay.

26:41.442 --> 26:43.467
0ne, two, three, four, five!

26:55.690 --> 26:56.987
Howdy, partners!

26:57.058 --> 27:00.152
Just remember, it´s Cowboy Day!

27:00.228 --> 27:01.820
l mean ´´Cowgirl´´!

27:02.764 --> 27:04.493
lt´s Cowpeople Day!

27:04.866 --> 27:07.391
Sit tall on your saddles.
Walk like you mean it.

27:07.468 --> 27:10.904
And remember, one person
in the Porta-Potty at a time.

27:11.239 --> 27:13.571
-Dawn?
-Thank you, Kristy.

27:16.244 --> 27:18.644
The Earth can do anything
if you treat it right.

27:18.713 --> 27:20.112
Howdy, Dawn!

27:21.482 --> 27:22.574
Alan!

27:24.052 --> 27:26.418
What did you do that for?

