before someone turned it into a greenhouse.

37:05.065 --> 37:08.330
lt´s owned by the town,
but the civic committee said if we fix it...

37:08.402 --> 37:10.495
and they approve it, we can use it.

37:10.571 --> 37:13.039
-lt´s awfully dirty.
-lt´s really cool.

37:13.407 --> 37:17.537
-l don´t know. lt seems like a lot of work.
-lt´s really hot in here.

37:17.611 --> 37:20.239
We´ve got the nebs for the grunt work.

37:20.481 --> 37:24.474
We can put the meeting table over there,
and the phone banks over there.

37:24.552 --> 37:27.544
Don´t you think this would make
an absolutely amazing office?

37:27.655 --> 37:30.283
Yeah, l do. That´s why l suggested it.

37:39.767 --> 37:41.598
No! Put that down!

37:42.536 --> 37:45.699
Anyone caught throwing food
will be sent to the time-out booth.

37:47.908 --> 37:50.399
Mallory, have you seen Dawn around?

37:50.744 --> 37:52.473
Yeah, she´s around.

37:53.214 --> 37:55.682
l repeat.: Anyone caught throwing food...

37:55.749 --> 37:58.343
will definitely be sent to the time-out booth.

37:58.819 --> 38:00.616
l didn´t do anything.

38:02.423 --> 38:05.722
All right! That´s it!
Everyone to the time-out booth!

38:06.227 --> 38:09.219
Cut it out! That´s it!
Come on! That´s enough!

38:10.998 --> 38:12.727
-l´m wiped.
-Dead.

38:12.800 --> 38:15.462
-Stace, how was your date with Luca?
-Smashing.

38:15.536 --> 38:18.869
Smashing? Did he hit you over the head
with his charm?

38:18.939 --> 38:22.534
My parents said we could use
my aunt´s cabin for Kristy´s birthday party.

38:22.610 --> 38:24.305
-Great.
-That´s perfect.

38:24.378 --> 38:28.906
Kristy, Watson told my stepdad he had some
