01:18:48.099 --> 01:18:50.226
l didn´t think l´d ever feel good again.

01:18:50.301 --> 01:18:53.293
l felt the same way
when my mom and dad split up.

01:18:54.773 --> 01:18:57.936
Me, too. lt´s the worst.

01:18:58.610 --> 01:19:01.773
l feel so stupid.
l really believed him this time.

