lt´s not your fault, Kristy.

01:19:06.918 --> 01:19:09.751
But l thought l was more important to him.

01:19:09.988 --> 01:19:11.888
You´re important to us.

01:19:12.857 --> 01:19:15.018
l screwed up your whole summer.

01:19:15.293 --> 01:19:17.784
Okay, so this summer was your turn.

01:19:19.130 --> 01:19:22.258
l can´t believe you guys
are still talking to me.

01:19:22.434 --> 01:19:24.561
Are you still talking to me?

01:19:25.870 --> 01:19:29.533
