01:19:35.880 --> 01:19:38.212
Okay, l guess l would´ve.

01:19:39.350 --> 01:19:40.749
Make a wish.

01:19:51.830 --> 01:19:53.422
Friends forever.

01:19:59.104 --> 01:20:00.401
You guys.

01:20:02.841 --> 01:20:05.275
What kind of cake is this, anyway?

01:20:09.013 --> 01:20:10.275
You guys.

01:20:14.619 --> 01:20:18.055
l can´t believe he was here for over a month
and you never told me.

01:20:18.123 --> 01:20:20.921
You think l liked not telling you?
lt was really hard.

01:20:20.992 --> 01:20:25.088
Well, l´m sure it was hard,
but that doesn´t make it right to lie.

01:20:25.163 --> 01:20:28.360
-He made me promise.
-He shouldn´t have done that.

01:20:28.600 --> 01:20:31.797
But he said on my birthday
we were going to tell you.

01:20:32.237 --> 01:20:35.172
l could wring his neck for doing this to you.

01:20:35.240 --> 01:20:38.004
Maybe if l´d been different,
he wouldn´t have done it.

01:20:38.076 --> 01:20:41.170
No, you´re not supposed
to be the grownup here.

01:20:41.980 --> 01:20:46.041
Your father says he´s gonna do
a lot of things that he doesn´t do.

01:20:46.718 --> 01:20:48.481
Why is he like that?

01:20:49.921 --> 01:20:51.684
Honey, l don´t know.

01:20:52.757 --> 01:20:54.486
l believed him, too.

01:20:54.959 --> 01:20:58.360
l´m glad we got to spend time together.
He made me laugh.

01:20:58.930 --> 01:21:00.124
l know.

01:21:00.765 --> 01:21:03.962
That´s one of the most wonderful things
about him.

01:21:04.669 --> 01:21:06.569
He loves you, you know.

01:21:06.805 --> 01:21:09.797
But not the way
you and Watson love me, right?

01:21:12.343 --> 01:21:14.675
This was in the mailbox for you.

01:21:19.350 --> 01:21:20.442
Wait.

01:21:23.621 --> 01:21:26.920
´´Dear Kristy,
l want to tell you this in person...

01:21:27.192 --> 01:21:30.252
´´but l don´t have the heart
or the guts, l guess.

01:21:30.361 --> 01:21:34.161
´´The job didn´t work out.
Can you believe it? After all that.

01:21:34.532 --> 01:21:38.366
´´Hope your birthday´s great.
Remember, l owe you a ride on The Monster.

01:21:38.436 --> 01:21:39.562
´´Love, Dad.

01:21:39.771 --> 01:21:42.331
´´PS: Seeing you meant everything to me.

01:21:42.440 --> 01:21:46.069
´´l´m so sorry l let you down
and put you in a tough spot with your mom.

01:21:46.144 --> 01:21:47.839
´´l´ll never do it again.

01:21:48.012 --> 01:21:50.105
´´l´m on my way to Colorado.

01:21:50.215 --> 01:21:54.811
´´Chris Almond told me there´s an opening
for a stringer on the paper there.´´

01:21:55.753 --> 01:21:58.187
