01:22:00.758 --> 01:22:03.022
Your father is full of dreams.

01:22:04.128 --> 01:22:05.618
Just like you.

01:22:08.733 --> 01:22:10.701
Don´t ever give them up.

01:22:16.541 --> 01:22:17.872
What happened?

01:22:18.042 --> 01:22:19.236
No!

01:22:19.377 --> 01:22:21.971
-What´s happening here?
-What´s going on?

01:22:25.817 --> 01:22:28.877
-What did they do to this place?
-What happened, Kristy?

01:22:28.953 --> 01:22:31.217
The civic committee is coming today.

01:22:31.356 --> 01:22:33.119
What are we gonna do?

01:22:33.191 --> 01:22:35.250
-We´re dead meat.
-My flowers!

01:22:35.326 --> 01:22:37.157
What´d they do to my paints?

01:22:37.228 --> 01:22:39.890
-Look at this mess.
-l can´t believe this.

01:22:39.964 --> 01:22:42.558
-Look at this place.
-lt´s disgusting.

01:22:43.534 --> 01:22:45.001
Don´t be sad.

01:22:48.406 --> 01:22:50.169
You guys! Look!

01:22:52.944 --> 01:22:55.208
lt´s like that thing in Hollywood.

01:22:55.313 --> 01:22:56.678
She melted.

01:22:56.881 --> 01:22:59.816
That girl is building up
some very bad karma.

01:23:02.520 --> 01:23:04.852
The civic committee
was coming in two hours.

01:23:04.923 --> 01:23:07.483
Cokie had really creamed us this time.

01:23:07.592 --> 01:23:10.823
Then Claud, using a very brilliant
scientific method...

01:23:10.895 --> 01:23:14.126
