01:30:29.367 --> 01:30:33.167
But l guess that´s what it takes sometimes
to really be a friend.

01:30:33.270 --> 01:30:36.728
Mom says, ´´lf you can count the number
of friends you have on one hand...

01:30:36.807 --> 01:30:38.172
´´that´s a lot. ´´

01:30:38.242 --> 01:30:41.405
l´ve got five fingers
and more than five friends.

01:30:42.413 --> 01:30:44.347
All right, everybody. Lean in.

01:30:44.448 --> 01:30:47.383
Mom says l´m way ahead. l think she´s right.

01:30:48.252 --> 01:30:49.810
And say, ´´trees.´´

01:30:49.887 --> 01:30:51.354
Trees!

