-l don´t know. What do you wanna do?

01:33:23.073 --> 01:33:26.338
-l don´t know. What do you wanna do?
-l don´t know. What should we do?

01:33:26.410 --> 01:33:28.139
-l don´t know.
-l don´t know, either!

01:33:28.212 --> 01:33:30.112
