01:33:30.180 --> 01:33:32.512
-Are you hungry?
-Yeah.

01:33:32.583 --> 01:33:34.676
-What do you wanna eat?
-l don´t know.

01:33:34.752 --> 01:33:36.242
l don´t know, either.

01:33:36.587 --> 01:33:38.418
-Where do you wanna go?
-l don´t know.

01:33:38.489 --> 01:33:39.751
l don´t know, either.

